  "detailed_description": "\"My lovely Pets 2\" is an exciting game, which offers interesting ways to find funny and playful pets, as well as bright hidden objects, and a set of popular mini-games. Meet and make friends with these funny pets in beautiful game locations where they are always ready to hide and fool around.<br />\r\nThis is a game with hidden objects and pets. Use your skills and knowledge to play mini-games and find all the hidden objects.            <br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe collector's edition includes:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n8 new locations where you can find even more cute animals!<br />\r\n8 new mini-games<br />\r\n8 additional mini-games from previous parts<br />\r\nBeautiful desktop wallpapers<br />\r\nMusic Player<br />\r\nShop with cute pets",
